        public void sessionClosed(java.lang.String sessionName,
                          AylaError error)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaSessionManager.SessionManagerListener
        Notifies that the session has been closed. If the session was closed due to an error, the error field will contain an AylaError with the reason for closure. If the session was closed because the user signed out, error will be null.
        指定者:
        sessionClosed 在接口中 AylaSessionManager.SessionManagerListener
        参数:
        sessionName - name of the session that was closed
        error - null for user sign-out, or the error that caused the closure of the session

                                   AylaAuthorization authorization)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaSessionManager.SessionManagerListener
        Notifies that the authorization has been refreshed. Applications that cache authorization data should update their cache with the new value.
